            <abstract>
                <p>A miniature illustrating <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3611Miracle"/> typically 
                    with as a sequence of six episodes/events, showing: first, Sofyā lying on top of a building before an icon of <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/>   holding Christ
                    while an <term key="angel">angel</term> carries away the child from her womb; second, the <term key="angel">angel</term>
                handing the child to Finkǝs; third, the bishop sitting on a throne in front of a group of women accusing Sofyā; fourth, the bishop and Sofyā
                sitting next to each other; fifth, the bishop sitting next to Finkǝs and the child; sixth, the child as a grown man surrounded by two persons.</p>
            </abstract>
